649,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/seven-sadaqah-al-jariyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32657,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Seven types of ongoing charity after death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeven deeds of a servant continue to be rewarded after his death while he is in his grave: knowledge to be learned, constructing a canal, digging a well, planting a date-palm tree, building a mosque,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13000,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/heavens-earth-praise-scholars\/","url_meta":{"origin":32657,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ilm: Heaven and earth praise seekers of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever travels a path in search of knowledge, Allah will make him traverse a path to Paradise. Verily, the angels lower their wings in pleasure for the seeker of knowledge. The inhabitants of the heavens and earth, even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37957,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/16\/dua-before-sleeping\/","url_meta":{"origin":32657,"position":2},"title":"Hadith o